ts/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番黎我身邊好唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />TPK"},{"pid":"86248f46660ba4780cd79c6d9f059d0da7fcc86a","tid":1127703,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"好似呼吸唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7169c2bdb648cf91c569d1bf2978d4b68097df","tid":1127703,"uid":58333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86248f46660ba4780cd79c6d9f059d0da7fcc86a","tid":1127703,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"好似呼吸唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"同意 每一下都要好用力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後又完全食唔落野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d5b9bd0489b5f869307505e1e67dc49fbe7d87","tid":1127703,"uid":248571,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"一諗起就會唔開心到反胃 食唔落嘢<br />\n開頭幾個月發夢會夢到佢<br />\n之後一晚醒幾次 冇原因<br />\n過咗一年終於成個人正常翻<br />\n諗起都係眉心開始緊同痛 同個人起雞皮<br />\n我好清楚我唔係討厭佢所以咁<br />\n而係太唔開心 心理影響咗生理<br />\n<br />\n年幾黎諗翻起覺得嗰陣負面情緒好嚴重<br />\n有懷疑其實唔開心到嘔係咪情緒病病徵"},{"pid":"5eba43c4f584469744f64fe0d09cc5495e77b358","tid":1127703,"uid":97872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"痛到想死<br />\n不斷諗返甜蜜嘅回憶<br />\n仲保留佢嘅相喺銀包<br />\n<br />\n但心知佢已經係你生命嘅過客"},{"pid":"d4dce501d284bcab4d4b69c4fe21b94b0d026cdb","tid":1127703,"uid":230595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"一個字 好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開心點解會分手？唔開心先會分手，分左手咪開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f3154